  "ai_help_text": "I can help you with:\n🌿 Product information\n📦 Packaging methods\n🚚 Shipping & logistics\n📋 Export documentation\n💰 Pricing queries\n\nHow can I help you today? 🌾",
  "ai_export_info": "Sure thing! 😊 For agricultural exports, all products must meet international phytosanitary standards.\n\nKey certifications we handle:\n✅ FSSAI\n✅ APEDA Registration\n✅ Phytosanitary Certificate\n✅ Certificate of Origin\n\nNeed help with a specific product? Just ask! 🌿",
